# ===== Facade repo: keep source + binaries OUT of git =====
# Source code must NOT be published (user opted to distribute binaries only)
src/
electron/
mcp/
scripts/

# Built installers / unpacked output (distributed via GitHub Releases, not git)
release/
dist/
dist-web/
build/

# Python (backend venv + caches; server source lives in server/ and IS committed)
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
server/__pycache__/

# Project-local data (not source, not for publish)
.workbuddy/

# electron-vite temp config leftovers (real config is electron.vite.config.ts)
electron.vite.config.*.mjs

# Binary installer extensions (safety net; release/ already ignored)
*.dmg
*.exe
*.AppImage
*.deb
*.zip
*.blockmap

# ===== Private / sensitive — must NOT be published =====
# 软著登记材料（含身份/申请材料）、合同模板、营销文案 —— 私密，不进公开仓库
软著登记材料/
软件开发合作协议书_模板.md
小红书文案_ChemThisTry.md

# Redundant pnpm files (project uses npm; package-lock.json is source of truth)
pnpm-lock.yaml
pnpm-workspace.yaml

# Security audit / hardening docs — keep internal, do not publish弱点细节
SECURITY_AUDIT.md
SECURITY_HARDENING_PLAN.md

# Software design spec — software-copyright material, keep local
ChemThisTry_软件设计说明书.txt
